item.description:
Get ready for bathing suit season with an outdoor bootcamp with Alex!
One hour of fitness Boot camp. All fitness levels welcome!


Location: McCulloch Building field (182 Green Street) MerryKnoll entrance

Cost: $13 ****CASH ONLY!!!*** This is outdoors with no CC machines available. Please try to bring exact change.


You will need a yoga mat and hand weights (3-8 pounds depending on your level) and your water!

Alternating aerobic intervals such as step, jump rope, kickbox, and athletic drills with strengthening intervals!!

Be prepared to work up a sweat. Bring some water and maybe even a towel!

(this event is also listed under Julie Hart Fitness and Boot Camps meetup group. Please do not double rsvp).
item.how_to_find_us: Merry Knoll St Entrance. Behind the building.
